<body>
<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="11500000t" end="42500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">事情感觉越来越奇妙了</p>
<p begin="42500000t" end="74600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">别这么操我老人家行吗</p>
<p begin="74600000t" end="105000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">真不晓得他们到底要我做什么</p>
<p begin="117200000t" end="130000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">不过或许…</p>
<p begin="130000000t" end="147200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">就是要我这种已经一脚踏入棺材的人</p>
<p begin="147200000t" end="166400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">才做得到某些事吧</p>
<p begin="175100000t" end="191000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">好啦 公主殿下</p>
<p begin="191000000t" end="222600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">我们知道的就是这些了</p>
<p begin="222600000t" end="241000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">还有什么想问的吗</p>
<p begin="241000000t" end="277300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">跟我事前知道的内容差不多呢</p>
<p begin="277300000t" end="309400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">不过有几点让我挺在意的</p>
<p begin="328500000t" end="361000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">做出能自己行动且危害周遭的人偶</p>
<p begin="361000000t" end="386500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">并不是那么简单的事</p>
<p begin="386500000t" end="422000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">若是由知名的制偶师倾力制作</p>
<p begin="422000000t" end="437800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">或长年被珍藏</p>
<p begin="437800000t" end="459200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">寄宿了物主思念的东西</p>
<p begin="459200000t" end="474600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">或许还有机会动起来</p>
<p begin="474600000t" end="504200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">但这次造成问题的木制人偶</p>
<p begin="504200000t" end="522500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">是由笨拙的门外汉制作</p>
<p begin="522500000t" end="542500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">而且大约一个月前才完成</p>
<p begin="546700000t" end="579200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">还能从手发出电击实在太不正常了</p>
<p begin="579200000t" end="596400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">如果一个老人的怨恨</p>
<p begin="596400000t" end="613500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">就能产生这种东西</p>
<p begin="613500000t" end="634700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">这世界肯定会更加混沌的</p>
<p begin="638900000t" end="661400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">这就是这次最令人不解的地方</p>
<p begin="661400000t" end="703100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">我认识一个可能做出那种超常怪物的人</p>
<p begin="711500000t" end="735300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">如果那个人在这件事背后操纵</p>
<p begin="735300000t" end="769000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">要处理那人偶就会有点棘手了</p>
<p begin="780600000t" end="799500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">我是不知道你们的状况</p>
<p begin="799500000t" end="819800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">但大概没有那种内情</p>
<p begin="819800000t" end="851200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">善太的人偶跟匹诺曹是一样的</p>
<p begin="851200000t" end="896700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">那人偶的材料里混着很特殊的东西</p>
<p begin="896700000t" end="912500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">特殊的东西?</p>
<p begin="912500000t" end="934500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">木偶奇遇记的木偶</p>
<p begin="934500000t" end="961700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">的确是用会动跟说话的木棒做成的</p>
<p begin="961700000t" end="994600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">善太倒是没有那么特殊的木头</p>
<p begin="994600000t" end="1014600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">不过材料本身还是挺特别的</p>
<p begin="1014600000t" end="1062300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">那人偶的一部分用了嵌着陨石的木材</p>
<p begin="1073400000t" end="1083900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">陨…?</p>
<p begin="1163500000t" end="1187000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">在四季中转瞬即逝之冬</p>
<p begin="1187000000t" end="1215300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">有位如雪般的美人</p>
<p begin="1215300000t" end="1237900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">折羽织缎只为祈愿</p>
<p begin="1237900000t" end="1266200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">落下泪珠化身为鹤</p>
<p begin="1266200000t" end="1288700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">踏上寻找世界尽头旅途</p>
<p begin="1288700000t" end="1317100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">沙漠中的少年</p>
<p begin="1317100000t" end="1339600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">释放了神灯的精灵</p>
<p begin="1339600000t" end="1368000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">获得无可取代的财富</p>
<p begin="1368000000t" end="1420000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">精巧隐瞒的真象 形同幻化</p>
<p begin="1420000000t" end="1454300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">之中能有什么意义?</p>
<p begin="1454300000t" end="1493800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">人生! 一切! 皆是! 神秘!</p>
<p begin="1509300000t" end="1553600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">让我们背对太阳</p>
<p begin="1553600000t" end="1607400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">轻轻为无形的未来染上色彩</p>
<p begin="1607400000t" end="1655800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">来杯刚泡好热腾腾的红茶吧</p>
<p begin="1655800000t" end="1684400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">宴会已经开始了</p>
<p begin="1684400000t" end="1718700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">快告诉我 夜色中的故事</p>
<p begin="1745000000t" end="1773700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">根据善太的说法 大概是在10年前</p>
<p begin="1779600000t" end="1807500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">当时他身体非常不好</p>
<p begin="1807500000t" end="1832100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">神经痛和偏头痛非常严重</p>
<p begin="1832100000t" end="1862500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">他便想着要自杀进了山里</p>
<p begin="1866300000t" end="1878100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">就在那时…</p>
<p begin="1974700000t" end="2009900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">善太说他马上就注意到那是个陨石</p>
<p begin="2009900000t" end="2053700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">发现刚落地的陨石是十分稀奇的事</p>
<p begin="2053700000t" end="2081500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">要是大众知道肯定会马上登上新闻</p>
<p begin="2081500000t" end="2116200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">但善太说他被陨石的奇妙魅力吸引</p>
<p begin="2116200000t" end="2147500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">就把它带回去放在身边</p>
<p begin="2152100000t" end="2168400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">不可思议的是</p>
<p begin="2168400000t" end="2203400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">在那之后 他的身体就日渐好转了</p>
<p begin="2212100000t" end="2245500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">于是他对那根嵌着陨石的木头越来越着迷</p>
<p begin="2245500000t" end="2266800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">非常珍惜地收藏着</p>
<p begin="2266800000t" end="2281800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">陨石自古以来</p>
<p begin="2281800000t" end="2302200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">因为是从天而降的特殊物体</p>
<p begin="2302200000t" end="2321800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">经常被视为信仰对象</p>
<p begin="2326300000t" end="2344000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">比如被视为来自上天的神谕</p>
<p begin="2344000000t" end="2382200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">或是作为奇迹的象征供奉在神殿中</p>
<p begin="2382200000t" end="2404900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">但陨石就只是陨石吧</p>
<p begin="2404900000t" end="2421500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">应该没有令人偶动起来</p>
<p begin="2421500000t" end="2455300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">或让手释放电击的力量</p>
<p begin="2455300000t" end="2475800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">大地拥有催生妖怪 精怪</p>
<p begin="2475800000t" end="2501900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">幽灵和魔物的力量</p>
<p begin="2501900000t" end="2520300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">它们对大多数人来说</p>
<p begin="2520300000t" end="2540800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">是相当不可思议的现象</p>
<p begin="2540800000t" end="2577900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">我们无法断言宇宙中没有类似的力量</p>
<p begin="2577900000t" end="2603700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">如果这力量寄宿在陨石中降落到地面</p>
<p begin="2603700000t" end="2627500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">受拾获陨石之人的意念 愿望影响的话</p>
<p begin="2627500000t" end="2647200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">也可能引发灾害</p>
<p begin="2653000000t" end="2675000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">可以说是来自宇宙的怪异呢</p>
<p begin="2705600000t" end="2723500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">善太在讲述陨石时</p>
<p begin="2723500000t" end="2751000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">大部分的人都当作笑话听听而已</p>
<p begin="2751000000t" end="2768900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">但他是认真的</p>
<p begin="2785100000t" end="2814300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">你做这人偶是想代替他吗</p>
<p begin="2814300000t" end="2843900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">你以为像匹诺曹一样用特别的木头做</p>
<p begin="2843900000t" end="2876900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">人偶就真能动起来吗</p>
<p begin="2897400000t" end="2930000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">这颗石头会实现我的愿望</p>
<p begin="2930000000t" end="2951200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">制作匹诺曹的老爷爷</p>
<p begin="2951200000t" end="2984200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">可是因为匹诺曹吃了很多苦头哦</p>
<p begin="2984200000t" end="3013700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">做出那种东西也不会有什么好事的</p>
<p begin="3030000000t" end="3060500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">我早就遇过够多衰事了</p>
<p begin="3060500000t" end="3097200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">他用嵌着陨石的木头做了右手</p>
<p begin="3097200000t" end="3127200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">所以才只能从右手发出电击吧</p>
<p begin="3127200000t" end="3139800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">多惠太太</p>
<p begin="3140100000t" end="3173500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">这么重要的事您怎么不早说呢</p>
<p begin="3173500000t" end="3195100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">说了又能怎么样呢</p>
<p begin="3201100000t" end="3210100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">要是早点知道</p>
<p begin="3210100000t" end="3232300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">咱们就不会鲁莽地去偷袭它了啊</p>
<p begin="3232300000t" end="3269400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">咱们怎么可能赢得了来自宇宙的怪异呢</p>
<p begin="3269400000t" end="3300600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">我也不知道你们都做了些什么啊</p>
<p begin="3300600000t" end="3333700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">居然还得应付宇宙奇象</p>
<p begin="3333700000t" end="3350000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">你也真是辛苦</p>
<p begin="3350000000t" end="3371200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">学长 你也别想跑</p>
<p begin="3371200000t" end="3387900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">来自宇宙的东西</p>
<p begin="3387900000t" end="3404500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">对这片土地就是异物</p>
<p begin="3404500000t" end="3435000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">想必与我们世界的秩序互不相容</p>
<p begin="3435000000t" end="3455800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">必须立刻排除才行</p>
<p begin="3455800000t" end="3473700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">比起有那个人牵涉其中</p>
<p begin="3473700000t" end="3493800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">现在的状况好懂多了</p>
<p begin="3493800000t" end="3518000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">善太先生在制作人偶时</p>
<p begin="3518000000t" end="3552200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">有具体说过要让它做什么吗</p>
<p begin="3552200000t" end="3561300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">没有</p>
<p begin="3571800000t" end="3583800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">这样啊</p>
<p begin="3583800000t" end="3626800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">他没有说是以 模仿匹诺曹的心态制作人偶的啊</p>
<p begin="3636400000t" end="3652300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">这有什么关联吗</p>
<p begin="3665200000t" end="3707700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">善太在人偶大致成形时曾这么说过</p>
<p begin="3711900000t" end="3775700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">这个人偶说不定能代替我实现我的心愿</p>
<p begin="3787500000t" end="3837000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">要是我那时能注意到他想做什么就好了</p>
<p begin="3837000000t" end="3865500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">就这么一点线索 谁都察觉不到的</p>
<p begin="3865500000t" end="3895000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">人偶会动起来 还拥有那样的力量</p>
<p begin="3895000000t" end="3911300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">就算是我也预测不到</p>
<p begin="3922500000t" end="3940000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">但你怎么一脸老神在在的样子</p>
<p begin="3940000000t" end="3949300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">继续放着不管的话</p>
<p begin="3949300000t" end="3976800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">那人偶迟早也会被镇民看见吧</p>
<p begin="3976800000t" end="3991300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">虽然一开始会害怕</p>
<p begin="3991300000t" end="4024300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">但大家肯定会一起想办法捕捉并破坏它</p>
<p begin="4024300000t" end="4033900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">要是如此</p>
<p begin="4033900000t" end="4061100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">真不晓得那电击会酿成多少灾情</p>
<p begin="4074300000t" end="4091100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">你打算怎么解决呢 公主殿下</p>
<p begin="4091100000t" end="4100600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">在我看来</p>
<p begin="4100600000t" end="4131900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">你似乎没有可以破坏那人偶的力量</p>
<p begin="4131900000t" end="4144400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">多 多惠太太</p>
<p begin="4144400000t" end="4166600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">公主殿下可是智慧之神</p>
<p begin="4166600000t" end="4204200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">当然不会长着擅用蛮力的外貌</p>
<p begin="4204200000t" end="4234200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">然而这次有九郎大人来助阵</p>
<p begin="4234200000t" end="4268700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">九郎大人可说是比怪物还骇人的怪物</p>
<p begin="4268700000t" end="4300800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">那种人偶肯定伸手一扭就能解决了啦</p>
<p begin="4319700000t" end="4345500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">就凭这一脸呆样的竹竿男吗</p>
<p begin="4345500000t" end="4361000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">您说得对</p>
<p begin="4361000000t" end="4370000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">我说</p>
<p begin="4370000000t" end="4401300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">九郎学长可是我经父母承认的情人</p>
<p begin="4401300000t" end="4426800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">请别这么尖酸刻薄地批评他</p>
<p begin="4434300000t" end="4444800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">情人...</p>
<p begin="4444800000t" end="4471100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">说是情人也太难听了</p>
<p begin="4471100000t" end="4483600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">明明就是事实</p>
<p begin="4483600000t" end="4508100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">而且有我这么可爱的少女当情人</p>
<p begin="4508100000t" end="4524400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">你有什么不满的</p>
<p begin="4524400000t" end="4549100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">都快二十岁的人了</p>
<p begin="4549100000t" end="4566600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">还自称少女也太不要脸了吧</p>
<p begin="4566600000t" end="4580400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">当然托学长的福</p>
<p begin="4580400000t" end="4596200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">我的确不算少女…</p>
<p begin="4606600000t" end="4633700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">你们的关系怎样都好啦</p>
<p begin="4633700000t" end="4645700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">总之有他在</p>
<p begin="4645700000t" end="4663300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">就能阻止那人偶了是吧</p>
<p begin="4673300000t" end="4697500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">就算没有九郎学长</p>
<p begin="4697500000t" end="4722500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">只是要破坏人偶的话 其实挺简单的</p>
<p begin="4722500000t" end="4744300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">你到底有没有把我的话听进去</p>
<p begin="4744300000t" end="4778800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">连怪物们都没办法靠近它耶</p>
<p begin="4783100000t" end="4806300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">你们说那人偶白天藏身山中</p>
<p begin="4806300000t" end="4850600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">到了晚上便会走同一条路从往海边移动</p>
<p begin="4855100000t" end="4888600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">然后经过这房子下方的沙滩</p>
<p begin="4893100000t" end="4911400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">而且就算很靠近</p>
<p begin="4911400000t" end="4932400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">它也不会攻击不动的东西</p>
<p begin="4932400000t" end="4943100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">对吧</p>
<p begin="4943100000t" end="4950600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">没错</p>
<p begin="4950600000t" end="4983700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">那么只要设陷阱埋伏就行了</p>
<p begin="4983700000t" end="5017500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">事前在沙滩的一定范围内埋炸药</p>
<p begin="5017500000t" end="5069500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">等人偶走到陷阱中央用遥控器引爆</p>
<p begin="5069500000t" end="5087500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">马上就能炸成碎片咯</p>
<p begin="5104200000t" end="5128400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">如果不方便取得炸药</p>
<p begin="5128400000t" end="5144700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">改用可燃物也可以</p>
<p begin="5149190000t" end="5162200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">在沙滩上大范围铺设可燃物</p>
<p begin="5162200000t" end="5207990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">等人偶走到范围内时点燃就行了</p>
<p begin="5207990000t" end="5226690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">像是从远处射燃烧的箭矢</p>
<p begin="5226690000t" end="5253500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">丢装满灯油的袋子来引燃</p>
<p begin="5253500000t" end="5278000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">就能确实地使人偶全身起火</p>
<p begin="5285100000t" end="5307300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">根本没有时间施展电击</p>
<p begin="5307300000t" end="5324400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">解决它的方法多的是</p>
<p begin="5345200000t" end="5377400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">我怎么没想到这么单纯的方法</p>
<p begin="5377400000t" end="5399500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">看来我也老得脑子不中用了</p>
<p begin="5399500000t" end="5423300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">是因为看到超乎常理的东西</p>
<p begin="5423300000t" end="5453700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">让你一时无法正常思考了吧</p>
<p begin="5453700000t" end="5467100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">这也没办法</p>
<p begin="5467100000t" end="5485300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">结果是我们大惊小怪了</p>
<p begin="5485300000t" end="5525900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">其实多动点脑子就能轻易破坏那人偶的</p>
<p begin="5525900000t" end="5551600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">正因如此我才觉得奇怪</p>
<p begin="5559700000t" end="5573400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">我不懂你的意思</p>
<p begin="5573400000t" end="5606300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">那人偶是孙子被撞死的善太先生</p>
<p begin="5606300000t" end="5628000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">想要复仇才制作的</p>
<p begin="5628000000t" end="5660500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">也就是善太先生的诅咒化成的实体</p>
<p begin="5660500000t" end="5687300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">但这样的话 您不觉得奇怪吗</p>
<p begin="5687300000t" end="5737700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">人偶应该会直接去杀撞死他孙子的人吧?</p>
<p begin="5748600000t" end="5763900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">的确是…</p>
<p begin="5769900000t" end="5804900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">当时车上的4个大学生虽然受到拘捕</p>
<p begin="5804900000t" end="5838700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">但被起诉的只有开车的那个人</p>
<p begin="5838700000t" end="5873700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">似乎也有证言指出 其他3人当时吵吵闹闹妨碍驾驶</p>
<p begin="5873700000t" end="5917500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">也没有积极协助抢救被害者</p>
<p begin="5922500000t" end="5951600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">而被起诉的人因为家中富裕</p>
<p begin="5951600000t" end="5972900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">支付了丰厚赔偿</p>
<p begin="5972900000t" end="6022500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">加上法院认为他有在反省 便判了缓刑</p>
<p begin="6022500000t" end="6042600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">但是这样的赔偿</p>
<p begin="6042600000t" end="6083000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">真的能让失去孩子的被害者遗族接受吗</p>
<p begin="6088800000t" end="6120100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">不 善太无法接受</p>
<p begin="6120100000t" end="6144400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">他一直恨着那几个大学生</p>
<p begin="6150700000t" end="6188900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">目前没传出那4个大学生离奇死亡的报道</p>
<p begin="6188900000t" end="6230800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">也就是说他们都未遭受人偶袭击</p>
<p begin="6230800000t" end="6262500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">真奇怪 那该怎么推断才对呢</p>
<p begin="6262500000t" end="6289600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">破坏人偶的方法多的是</p>
<p begin="6289600000t" end="6334100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">因为善太先生是故意做来让镇民破坏的</p>
<p begin="6340400000t" end="6352900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">如果是这样的话</p>
<p begin="6363700000t" end="6415900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">直接破坏人偶恐怕会带来无法挽回的后果</p>
<p begin="6415900000t" end="6438500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">可惜我是不会让他得逞的</p>
<p begin="6508500000t" end="6550700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">(或许是寄予星星的愿望)</p>
<p begin="6608600000t" end="6622400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">你走海边</p>
<p begin="6622400000t" end="6640200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">你们往陆地去</p>
<p begin="6640200000t" end="6682000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">人偶靠近也绝对别动 知道了吗</p>
<p begin="6690800000t" end="6711600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">真是奇妙的光景</p>
<p begin="6770000000t" end="6801600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">看来你也为那个公主殿下吃了不少苦头吧</p>
<p begin="6801600000t" end="6814700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">不好说呢</p>
<p begin="6814700000t" end="6829700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">毕竟如果没有她</p>
<p begin="6829700000t" end="6868500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">我现在或许会不知道该怎么活下去</p>
<p begin="6888500000t" end="6931000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">能用死亡决定未来是什么感觉</p>
<p begin="6931000000t" end="6951900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">虽然说是能决定未来</p>
<p begin="6951900000t" end="6984800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">其实只是让有可能的事情必定发生</p>
<p begin="6989800000t" end="7020700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">触及不了可能性很低的未来</p>
<p begin="7020700000t" end="7044500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">即便如此你仍有让公主殿下准备的陷阱</p>
<p begin="7044500000t" end="7078700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">一定会成功的力量吗</p>
<p begin="7078700000t" end="7100800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">虽然岩永她就算没有我帮忙</p>
<p begin="7100800000t" end="7134100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">八成也能靠自己的运气成功吧</p>
<p begin="7144100000t" end="7171600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">我也觉得她是绝对不能与之为敌的人物</p>
<p begin="7171600000t" end="7180000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">学长</p>
<p begin="7200400000t" end="7220000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">人偶走进海岸了</p>
<p begin="7220000000t" end="7250000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">应该再几分钟就会到这附近</p>
<p begin="7250000000t" end="7273500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">麻烦学长也就定位吧</p>
<p begin="7273500000t" end="7295100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">我在那里做了记号</p>
<p begin="7295100000t" end="7330100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">请诱导人偶走到那里去</p>
<p begin="7330100000t" end="7360100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">之后就由你觉得恰当的时机打个暗号</p>
<p begin="7371100000t" end="7403900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">还有…请尽量别死</p>
<p begin="7422400000t" end="7438900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">事到如今还提这个做什么</p>
<p begin="7438900000t" end="7466200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">不 是因为妖怪们似乎在传…</p>
<p begin="7466200000t" end="7526200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">说我是男友死掉几次都无所谓的冷酷之人</p>
<p begin="7526200000t" end="7539000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">这是事实吧</p>
<p begin="7539000000t" end="7557100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">就算知道你会马上复活</p>
<p begin="7557100000t" end="7578700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">我还是有点介意的好吗</p>
<p begin="7578700000t" end="7591600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">好好好</p>
<p begin="7596200000t" end="7610400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">只有一点吗…</p>
<p begin="7662500000t" end="7697500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">来看看公主殿下的预测能有几分准确吧</p>
<p begin="7697500000t" end="7735100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">我可是默认最糟糕的状况来拟定对策的</p>
<p begin="7882700000t" end="7913700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">人偶自古以来 不分东西洋文化</p>
<p begin="7913700000t" end="7942800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">都是做来进行咒术类的物品</p>
<p begin="7942800000t" end="7970800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">让神明或灵魂附身其中的描述</p>
<p begin="7970800000t" end="7990300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">可说是不胜枚举</p>
<p begin="7995000000t" end="8019600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">常见的有代替人类承受灾难</p>
<p begin="8019600000t" end="8044100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">或是遵从命令进行劳务等功用</p>
<p begin="8044100000t" end="8073400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">匹诺曹的童话也是这种类型</p>
<p begin="8073400000t" end="8101000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">然而 听见人偶与咒术</p>
<p begin="8101000000t" end="8135100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">应该还有另一个能马上想到的有名用法吧</p>
<p begin="8141700000t" end="8151700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">难道…</p>
<p begin="8151700000t" end="8177300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">没错 就是诅咒人偶</p>
<p begin="8181900000t" end="8206400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">以丑时参拜知名的稻草人为例</p>
<p begin="8206400000t" end="8236400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">是用五寸钉把草人钉在神社境内的树木上</p>
<p begin="8236400000t" end="8253900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">来加害诅咒对象</p>
<p begin="8258200000t" end="8276500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">大部分的诅咒人偶</p>
<p begin="8276500000t" end="8297700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">会写上怨恨对象的名字</p>
<p begin="8297700000t" end="8314000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">贴上肖像或照片</p>
<p begin="8314000000t" end="8334500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">或是埋入对象的毛发 指甲</p>
<p begin="8334500000t" end="8362100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">这些与该名人物有关联的东西</p>
<p begin="8367100000t" end="8397100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">借此使人偶的存在等同于诅咒对象</p>
<p begin="8397100000t" end="8414600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">引发用钉子钉人偶时</p>
<p begin="8414600000t" end="8434600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">对象在相同部位感到疼痛</p>
<p begin="8443700000t" end="8465000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">折断人偶的手时 对象的手也折断</p>
<p begin="8465000000t" end="8476200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">把人偶丢入火里</p>
<p begin="8476200000t" end="8502500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">对象也跟着燃烧的现象</p>
<p begin="8515000000t" end="8541000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">善太先生制作的人偶也是这种类型</p>
<p begin="8683900000t" end="8696500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">因为它会擅自走动</p>
<p begin="8696500000t" end="8732700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">从手部释放电击 为城镇带来灾害</p>
<p begin="8732700000t" end="8757800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">所以很难令人想到它其实是个诅咒人偶</p>
<p begin="8757800000t" end="8784000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">但只要这样想 一切就都合理了</p>
<p begin="8996000000t" end="9014800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">善太先生的人偶中</p>
<p begin="9014800000t" end="9061900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">大概掺入了能连结撞死他孙子的 那4个大学生的东西</p>
<p begin="9066900000t" end="9082400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">要是随意破坏人偶</p>
<p begin="9082400000t" end="9114900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">大学生们恐怕就要没命了</p>
<p begin="9203700000t" end="9230800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">善太先生不只憎恨那4个大学生</p>
<p begin="9230800000t" end="9258700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">也恨着这城镇的人们</p>
<p begin="9258700000t" end="9281200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">但他没有亲手杀人的胆量</p>
<p begin="9281200000t" end="9305400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">也没坚强到足以承担谋杀的责任</p>
<p begin="9309200000t" end="9322200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">所以才想让镇民</p>
<p begin="9322200000t" end="9359200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">替他承担杀害4个大学生的罪孽</p>
<p begin="9359200000t" end="9388500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">只要人偶危害城镇</p>
<p begin="9388500000t" end="9414400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">镇民就会试图破坏人偶</p>
<p begin="9419800000t" end="9446100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">害死善太先生孙子的人们</p>
<p begin="9446100000t" end="9474800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">将会透过人偶承受强烈的憎恨</p>
<p begin="9474800000t" end="9498900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">而且那不仅是善太先生一个人的份</p>
<p begin="9498900000t" end="9546200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">是整个城镇的憎恨带来的强烈痛苦</p>
<p begin="9546200000t" end="9580800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">接着 当人偶被破坏时</p>
<p begin="9580800000t" end="9604500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">4个大学生将离奇死亡</p>
<p begin="9604500000t" end="9625000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">一旦这件事被传到镇上</p>
<p begin="9625000000t" end="9661200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">想必镇民们会默默感受到事情的关联</p>
<p begin="9661200000t" end="9684100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">在心中留下深刻的阴影吧</p>
<p begin="9690000000t" end="9705000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">而善太先生自己</p>
<p begin="9705000000t" end="9745900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">则能以没有亲自下手开脱</p>
<p begin="9745900000t" end="9783500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">害死鱼群 使城镇经济衰退</p>
<p begin="9783500000t" end="9798000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">已经是相当严重的诅咒了</p>
<p begin="9798000000t" end="9831300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">而让镇民代替自己背负杀人罪恶</p>
<p begin="9831300000t" end="9846400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">更是另一层诅咒</p>
<p begin="9846400000t" end="9863600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">这可说是出于无法背负罪孽的软弱…</p>
<p begin="9863600000t" end="9882600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">身为善人的本性</p>
<p begin="9882600000t" end="9906900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">绞尽脑汁想出来的方法</p>
<p begin="9911900000t" end="9959500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">然而最终呈现的样貌 反而比任何一种报复都更加不祥</p>
<p begin="9963700000t" end="9985800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">这样我们不就无从下手了吗</p>
<p begin="9985800000t" end="10004900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">难道你要破坏人偶</p>
<p begin="10004900000t" end="10050800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">代替镇民背负害死大学生们的罪吗</p>
<p begin="10050800000t" end="10080300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">我并不在意谁会背负罪恶感</p>
<p begin="10080300000t" end="10108700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">也不在乎这个城镇会有多少损失</p>
<p begin="10117500000t" end="10143700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">亏她顶着一张可爱的脸 竟如此无情</p>
<p begin="10143700000t" end="10168800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">不过善太先生的行为</p>
<p begin="10168800000t" end="10187900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">会搅乱这片土地的秩序</p>
<p begin="10192500000t" end="10242300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">因为他想借助从天外来的东西实现愿望</p>
<p begin="10242300000t" end="10262300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">不 这个公主殿下…</p>
<p begin="10265890000t" end="10303490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">既然如此 我就不能让他如愿</p>
<p begin="10303490000t" end="10327700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">长得楚楚可怜 个性却十分严酷</p>
<p begin="10339000000t" end="10352000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">我已经想到办法了</p>
<p begin="10352000000t" end="10379500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">从人偶身上拆掉连系诅咒的东西</p>
<p begin="10379500000t" end="10398590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">之后再破坏人偶</p>
<p begin="10398590000t" end="10424900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">被诅咒的对象就不会遭受危害了吧</p>
<p begin="10722600000t" end="10730200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">就是现在</p>
<p begin="11063000000t" end="11086400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">只是要让人偶掉进陷阱的话很简单</p>
<p begin="11086400000t" end="11118500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">但要像这样只绑住右手吊起来</p>
<p begin="11118500000t" end="11148100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">没有九郎学长的能力恐怕很难办到呢</p>
<p begin="11153100000t" end="11177400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">右肩或手肘说不定会松脱</p>
<p begin="11177400000t" end="11201600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">妖怪们 照事前说的把它埋住吧</p>
<p begin="11248200000t" end="11259500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">九郎学长</p>
<p begin="11280000000t" end="11293600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">请调查人偶</p>
<p begin="11293600000t" end="11335000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">有没有连系诅咒 埋入咒术素材的痕迹</p>
<p begin="11335000000t" end="11345800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">知道了</p>
<p begin="11400000000t" end="11441800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">四肢可能会有固定关节的零件松脱的风险</p>
<p begin="11441800000t" end="11465100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">所以我想应该是在躯干的部分</p>
<p begin="11485500000t" end="11515500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">这附近刻了好几个人名</p>
<p begin="11520100000t" end="11544000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">是那4个大学生的名字…</p>
<p begin="11554800000t" end="11578500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">还有另一个名字</p>
<p begin="11578500000t" end="11589900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">另一个?</p>
<p begin="11619500000t" end="11635200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">是我的名字吧</p>
<p begin="11668200000t" end="11707500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">善太大概无法接受 我好像过着很幸福的生活吧</p>
<p begin="11727500000t" end="11745800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">要怎么消除这些名字?</p>
<p begin="11745800000t" end="11764200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">直接刮掉吧</p>
<p begin="11764200000t" end="11798800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">虽然被指名的人或许会觉得痛</p>
<p begin="11798800000t" end="11821800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">不过这点痛苦是该忍受的</p>
<p begin="11821800000t" end="11836400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">当然我也是</p>
<p begin="11971500000t" end="11991000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">根本不痛不痒</p>
<p begin="12001500000t" end="12032400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">看来那个奇怪陨石和善太的执念</p>
<p begin="12032400000t" end="12068200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">只够让人偶行动和释放电击</p>
<p begin="12068200000t" end="12094900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">没能让那诅咒生效吧</p>
<p begin="12112800000t" end="12130700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">那么善太先生的企图</p>
<p begin="12130700000t" end="12162100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">打一开始就失败了呢</p>
<p begin="12162100000t" end="12190800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">被刻上名字的大学生们没有危险</p>
<p begin="12190800000t" end="12217200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">我的作战其实也没有意义</p>
<p begin="12220800000t" end="12255800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">这也算是害人终害己吗</p>
<p begin="12255800000t" end="12270900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">谁知道呢</p>
<p begin="12288000000t" end="12323000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">缜密却又得依靠他人才能完成的计划</p>
<p begin="12323000000t" end="12359800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">本来就很容易失败 这也是理所当然</p>
<p begin="12359800000t" end="12386900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">虽然这听起来也挺讽刺的</p>
<p begin="12393500000t" end="12416900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">您要协助破坏人偶吗</p>
<p begin="12416900000t" end="12443100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">体恤一下老人家行吗</p>
<p begin="12443100000t" end="12456600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">我要回去休息了</p>
<p begin="12514500000t" end="12535700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">我曾有过两个孩子</p>
<p begin="12543600000t" end="12586700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">但两人都在小时候就车祸身亡</p>
<p begin="12586700000t" end="12620000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">肇事者很富有 赔了一大笔钱给我们</p>
<p begin="12620000000t" end="12650400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">尽管被判了刑 也是一下子就出狱了</p>
<p begin="12650400000t" end="12694700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">我们夫妇则因此突然在这乡下成了资产家</p>
<p begin="12699700000t" end="12720500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">我们本来就生活无虞</p>
<p begin="12720500000t" end="12755500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">心想把这种钱留在手边也不会有好事</p>
<p begin="12755500000t" end="12787600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">因此当丈夫的朋友说想创业时</p>
<p begin="12787600000t" end="12808500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">便几乎把那笔赔偿金全投了进去</p>
<p begin="12808500000t" end="12839400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">没想到那公司竟飞速成长</p>
<p begin="12839400000t" end="12877700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">投资的钱翻了好几倍回到我们手上</p>
<p begin="12877700000t" end="12896100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">真是太讽刺了</p>
<p begin="12896100000t" end="12920700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">于是我们捐款给事故孤儿基金会等等</p>
<p begin="12920700000t" end="12947500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">总之试着把那笔钱用掉</p>
<p begin="12947500000t" end="12965300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">结果怎么花都花不完</p>
<p begin="12965300000t" end="12999200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">等到终于剩下心安理得的金额时</p>
<p begin="12999200000t" end="13027900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">这次换我丈夫碰上意外溺死了</p>
<p begin="13027900000t" end="13061300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">他比我小10岁 当时才50几岁呢</p>
<p begin="13067900000t" end="13104700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">结果我又因为意外得到大笔赔偿金</p>
<p begin="13104700000t" end="13140900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">光是要想怎么打理这笔钱就费尽了心力</p>
<p begin="13140900000t" end="13182600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">不过大家在暗地里都说 我是靠家人的死赚大钱的魔女什么的</p>
<p begin="13182600000t" end="13196500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">从善太眼里看来</p>
<p begin="13196500000t" end="13226000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">我应该是必须被否定的存在吧</p>
<p begin="13226000000t" end="13249400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">因为家人之死过着幸福生活的我</p>
<p begin="13249400000t" end="13269500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">必须是错误的</p>
<p begin="13269500000t" end="13305600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">不然就会显得他的行为实在太过愚蠢</p>
<p begin="13305600000t" end="13342400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">所以他才会也把我的名字刻在那人偶上吧</p>
<p begin="13347500000t" end="13373600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">迁怒也该有个限度吧</p>
<p begin="13373600000t" end="13409600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">像我也经常被说是得天独厚的人</p>
<p begin="13409600000t" end="13461700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">但我也正在经历名为 "心爱恋人不给我半点爱"的不幸啊</p>
<p begin="13461700000t" end="13479200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">是吗</p>
<p begin="13487200000t" end="13514300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">虽然这么说 过着衣食无虞的生活</p>
<p begin="13514300000t" end="13535500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">独自一人仍旧撑了下来的我</p>
<p begin="13535500000t" end="13550900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">的确称不上不幸</p>
<p begin="13562200000t" end="13604400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">不过 失去孩子和丈夫的时候</p>
<p begin="13604400000t" end="13636000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">我都曾失去活下去的动力</p>
<p begin="13646900000t" end="13681500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">我只不过是没有独自赴死的勇气罢了</p>
<p begin="13681500000t" end="13707000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">我在某种意义上也和善太一样</p>
<p begin="13707000000t" end="13733200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">害怕自己承担责任</p>
<p begin="13733200000t" end="13774100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">明明这家中早已没有任何我所珍惜的事物</p>
<p begin="13774100000t" end="13800300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">我却没有主动离去的勇气</p>
<p begin="13800300000t" end="13824200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">看见那人偶出现时</p>
<p begin="13824200000t" end="13847500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">我忍不住想这会不会是命中注定</p>
<p begin="13847500000t" end="13880000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">我就是为了阻止它 为了拯救城镇才活到现在的</p>
<p begin="13885400000t" end="13938900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414">是不是该牺牲自己和那人偶玉石俱焚…</p>
<p begin="13943900000t" end="13962200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415">结果全是我的妄想罢了</p>
<p begin="13962200000t" end="13974300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416">就算没有我</p>
<p begin="13974300000t" end="13994300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417">那东西依旧轻易被破坏掉了</p>
<p begin="13994300000t" end="14024400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418">我不过就是没有意义地停留在这里而已</p>
<p begin="14024400000t" end="14058100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419">不 多亏您在这里</p>
<p begin="14058100000t" end="14093500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420">我今天才能吃到这么好吃的早餐</p>
<p begin="14093500000t" end="14112000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421">说多少感谢都不够呢</p>
<p begin="14126000000t" end="14138600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422">真是谢谢你啊</p>
<p begin="14138600000t" end="14152700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423">不过那碗味噌汤</p>
<p begin="14152700000t" end="14189100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424">只是用公主殿下你带来的调理包泡的哦</p>
<p begin="14189500000t" end="14205000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425">就算如此也是感谢</p>
<p begin="14221100000t" end="14239600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426">没想到陨石跟一个老人的执念</p>
<p begin="14239600000t" end="14258800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427">竟然会生出那种人偶</p>
<p begin="14258800000t" end="14274600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428">这世界真是不可思议</p>
<p begin="14274600000t" end="14290000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle429">不好说呢</p>
<p begin="14290000000t" end="14313800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle430">说不定原因不只如此</p>
<p begin="14313800000t" end="14357900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle431">我从这颗陨石也没感受到多强烈的力量</p>
<p begin="14357900000t" end="14387600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle432">说不定嶋井多惠太太的执念</p>
<p begin="14387600000t" end="14417600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle433">也是驱动人偶的原动力之一</p>
<p begin="14417600000t" end="14441900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle434">你又在乱说谎…</p>
<p begin="14441900000t" end="14475600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle435">我这次可没有故意说谎哦</p>
<p begin="14475600000t" end="14498100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle436">那个人期盼着死亡</p>
<p begin="14498100000t" end="14532700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle437">而且必须是有意义的死亡</p>
<p begin="14532700000t" end="14560200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle438">说不定她下意识祈求着</p>
<p begin="14560200000t" end="14593200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle439">那人偶能对城镇带来灾害</p>
<p begin="14593200000t" end="14619600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle440">并由自己来赌命解决这件事</p>
<p begin="14637800000t" end="14653200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle441">所以人偶才能</p>
<p begin="14653200000t" end="14690400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle442">获得光凭善太先生的执念得不到的力量</p>
<p begin="14700400000t" end="14732200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle443">那个人到底幸不幸福呢</p>
<p begin="14732200000t" end="14766800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle444">这不是我们可以评判的事</p>
<p begin="14772200000t" end="14780900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle445">比起那个</p>
<p begin="14780900000t" end="14799300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle446">今天也还有时间</p>
<p begin="14799300000t" end="14823400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle447">绕点路去观光一下吧</p>
<p begin="14823400000t" end="14848000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle448">我来的时候就已经看好地点了</p>
<p begin="14848000000t" end="14865100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle449">像这里或这里…</p>
<p begin="14879400000t" end="14900200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle450">你看起来倒是挺幸福的 真好</p>
<p begin="14900200000t" end="14913500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle451">你那是什么语气</p>
<p begin="14913500000t" end="14937400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle452">把我说得像是神经大条的笨蛋一样</p>
<p begin="14937400000t" end="14947400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle453">难道不是吗?</p>
<p begin="14947400000t" end="14958100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle454">什么!</p>
<p begin="14970600000t" end="15000700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle455">(待续)</p>
